			  </div>
			  <div class="card-body bg-warning">
				<p class="card-text">Our foremost focus is on the academic growth and understanding. Regular classes are being conducted. Regular classes are being conducted.
								     Notebooks, text-books, stationary and other necessary facilities are being made available to our students free of cost which they otherwise 
									 could not afford to posses. Subjects like English, Mathamatics and Science are being taught to develop and improve general understanding of the
									 topics among students by presenting them with real life examples. This helps them develop an educational perspective of their surroundings
									 hygiene, introduce them with social etiquettes. Workshops are organized every saturday to let students engage their creative minds and to let
									 explore their intellectual depth.</p>
			  </div>
